casebody.data:
Buckler v. Senefeld. [No. 10,174. Filed November 21, 1919.] From Franklin Circuit Court; Raymond 8. Springer, Judge. I. N. McCarty, for appellant.

Action between Gifford Buckler and Mary Senefeld. From "the judgment rendered, the former appeals.

Affirmed.

Per Curiam. — Judgment affirmed.
